{"tid":1227344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個紙鶴，一人一個祝福","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:23:08.000Z","uid":34232,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e48c31b8f115d794377c72eecf2fab25fbe85a73","tid":1227344,"uid":34232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7s0s0zc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7s0s0zc.png&h=c1f52c25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"878d457d6cbb17672ff16e25e3276457aaa2d118","tid":1227344,"uid":34232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"一切嚟得都是那麼諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n當佢企喺天台嘅時候，<br />\n我哋嘅特首仲係對住傳媒美化自己。<br />\n<br />\n冇一個人care佢嘅生命。<br />\n<br />\n香港人嘅生命，<br />\n<br />\n一啲都唔值錢。"},{"pid":"7a57cdd6b7f6f3f8021544708149a05ad65e07a2","tid":1227344,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e391ce6f4704244b9462ffbf315dbaf5a2cd07e","tid":1227344,"uid":3195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"同埋白花"},{"pid":"c43953a70a708c48018e2198b708b8352181b864","tid":1227344,"uid":34232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e391ce6f4704244b9462ffbf315dbaf5a2cd07e","tid":1227344,"uid":3195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"同埋白花"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"最重要嘅，係一份心意。"},{"pid":"cc1196499732b6a5d656c9755bfccb6afc89b37a","tid":1227344,"uid":34232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"唔講政治，無論立場如何。<br />\n淨係希望大家，能當佢只係一個香港人。<br />\n<br />\n用實際行動，畀返佢一個尊嚴。"},{"pid":"abe863ca34cbfac97c75209d0523aee2b44ac434","tid":1227344,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"好"}]}